title: Police launch search after woman goes over Niagara Falls
text:
Niagara Falls - Police say they have launched a search after a woman went over Niagara Falls.
It happened around 18:00 on Saturday.
New York State Park Police say a woman in her 40s went over the falls at Prospect Point.
Park Police spokesman Randy Simons says it appeared the woman intentionally entered the water to "harm herself."
